---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="FAQ" description="Frequently asked questions (Educational content only; not medical advice).">
  <section class="card" style="padding:22px">
    <div class="kicker">FAQ</div>
    <h1 class="h1">Frequently asked questions</h1>

    <div class="hr"></div>

    <h2 class="h2">Are these products medical treatments?</h2>
    <p class="small">No. We use structure/function language. Educational content only; not medical advice.</p>

    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-top:14px">Why extracts?</h2>
    <p class="small">Extracts can improve consistency and make it easier to formulate within capsule-size constraints, depending on specifications.</p>

    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-top:14px">Are products vegan or kosher?</h2>
    <p class="small">Capsules are designed to be vegan. Kosher certification depends on manufacturer certification and ingredient sourcing.</p>

    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-top:14px">How do I access dossiers?</h2>
    <p class="small">Visit the Research Library and download PDFs. Some may be released in stages.</p>

    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-top:14px">Can I take these with medications?</h2>
    <p class="small">If you take medications or have conditions, consult a qualified clinician. We provide conservative safety notes in dossiers.</p>

    <div class="hr"></div>
    <div class="small">
      <strong>FDA disclaimer:</strong> These statements have not been evaluated by the FDA. Products are not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease.
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
